parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear backup camera can cause a lack of visibility when reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries to pedestrians, cyclists, or other vehicles.
symptoms: The rear backup camera display is black or blank
the camera image is distorted or flickering
the camera fails to display an image when the vehicle is in reverse
the camera wiring harness is damaged or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause the rear backup camera to malfunction or fail, leading to a lack of visibility when reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries to pedestrians, cyclists, or other vehicles.
symptoms: The wiring harness is damaged or broken
wires are pinched or severed
the camera image is distorted or flickering
the camera fails to display an image when the vehicle is in reverse.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic stop/start feature can cause the vehicle to shift into neutral unexpectedly, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into neutral unexpectedly
the engine shuts off
the vehicle fails to restart
the dash lights illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rearview camera can cause a blind spot, making it difficult or impossible to see objects or people behind the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rearview camera display is black
the camera image is intermittent
the camera image flickers
the camera stops working
the screen only shows yellow guide lines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tailgate wire harness can cause the rearview camera to malfunction, leading to a blind spot and increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rearview camera display is black
the camera image is intermittent
the camera stops working
the screen only shows yellow guide lines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the driver mirror can cause a blind spot, making it difficult or impossible to see objects or people behind the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The driver mirror requires frequent readjustment
the mirror image is wavy and distorted.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The spontaneous explosion of the sunroof can cause injury to the driver or passengers, as well as distractions that can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof shatters or explodes without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission and Auto Idle Shut-Off Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the transmission and auto idle shut-off system can cause the vehicle to roll backwards, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The transmission shifts from drive to neutral without warning
the vehicle rolls backwards without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the rear window switch can cause inconvenience and distraction, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear window switch does not function on demand
the switch functions intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning auto high-beam headlight system can cause distractions to both the driver and oncoming traffic, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The auto high-beam feature flickers on and off intermittently
fails to engage high-beam headlights when appropriate
disengages quickly
stays on for incoming traffic
dims unnecessarily for road signs or reflections
and fails to dim quickly enough for oncoming traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: LED Headlight Snow and Ice Accumulation
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Snow and ice accumulation on LED headlights can reduce visibility, causing safety risks for the driver and other road users.
symptoms: LED headlights become covered in snow and ice
requiring frequent manual clearing to maintain proper visibility.
